quran[8{c,v,t}:
11,46,"jawab mein irshad howa"" ae Nooh, woh tairay ghar walon mein se nahi hai, woh to aik bigra howa kaam hai, lehaza to uss baat ki mujh se darkhwast nah kar jis ki haqeeqat to nahi jaanta, mein tujhe nasiyaat karta hon ke apne aap ko jahilon ki terhan nah bana le """
11,47,"Nooh ne foran arz kya"" ae mere rab, mein teri panah mangta hon iss se ke woh cheez tujh se maanguu jis ka mujhe ilm nahi agar to ne mujh maaf nah kya aur reham nah farmaya to mein barbaad ho jaoon ga """
11,48,"hukum howa"" ae Nooh utar ja, hamari taraf se salamti aur barkaten hain tujh par aur un garohoon par jo tairay sath hain, aur kuch giroh aisay bhi hain jin ko hum kuch muddat samaan zindagi bakhsheen ge phir inhen hamari taraf se dard naak azaab puhanche ga """
11,49,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yeh ghaib ki khabrain hain jo hum tumhari taraf wahi kar rahay hain is se pehlay nah tum un ko jantay thay aur nah tumhari qoum, pas sabr karo, a Najjan car Muttaqiyun hi ke haq mein hai"
11,50,"aur Aad ki taraf hum ne un ke bhai hood ko bheja uss ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, Allah ki bandagi karo, tumhara koi khuda uss ke siwa nahi hai tum ne mehez jhoot ghurr rakhay hain"
11,51,"ae baradran qoum, is kaam par mein tum se koi ajar nahi chahta, mera ajar to is ke zimma hai jis ne mujhe peda kya hai, kya tum aqal se zara kaam nahi letay ?"
11,52,"aur ae meri qoum ke logo, apne rab se maffi chaho, phir is ki taraf paltoo, woh tum par aasman ke dhanay khol day ga aur tumhari mojooda qowat par mazeed qowat ka izafah kere ga mujrimon ki terhan mun nah phero """
11,53,"unhon ne jawab diya"" ae hood, to hamaray paas koi Sarih shahadat le kar nahi aaya hai, aur tairay kehnay se hum apne mabodon ko nahi chore satke, aur tujh par hum imaan laane walay nahi hain"
